景<br />\n暫時覺得Fijifilm同Olympus色好似幾靚<br />\n謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n富賤執相你就喊了<br />\n越執越柒永遠執唔到jpeg同樣色<br />\n而且jpeg係直出唔到<br />\n因勁多死黑死白<br />\n夜晚可以收工第一冇ois防手震第二由iso控制dr<br />\n推高iso連光位都爆鳩哂<br />\n最重要一點係富賤係抹noise細微位全抹鳩哂你<br />\n影景會冇咁忽影人連眼袋都冇鳩埋全抹走<br />\n剩返個滑劣劣圖像<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i1376.photobucket.com/albums/ah10/blankcathk/011924_551969c59e1dcfa06dbfa820fe0c654f_zpshbgepczy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1376.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fah10%2Fblankcathk%2F011924_551969c59e1dcfa06dbfa820fe0c654f_zpshbgepczy.jpg&h=b4c85efa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i1376.photobucket.com/albums/ah10/blankcathk/R52D7OQ_zpslugbx0nz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1376.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fah10%2Fblankcathk%2FR52D7OQ_zpslugbx0nz.jpg&h=d6f63ac2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你尼兩張係用咩機影？</blockquote><br />\n用富賤架好撚多死黑 好撚靚吧？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁巴打有咩推介？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係都要問佢的話<br />\n我幫下佢答你<br />\n請買sony旗艦機<br />\n但你得5000蚊<br />\n我建議你買sony電話影<br />\n包靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n先達有貨"},{"pid":"103e44f1b22e10fb406c52b363b4ca97a39dd27d","tid":296814,"uid":40461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T07:59:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果無反入門大家有咩推介 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n筆值大概5000左右<br />\n主要想影街景同夜景<br />\n暫時覺得Fijifilm同Olympus色好似幾靚<br />\n謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一部好相機係可以高度還原現實中的色彩<br />\n如果你話部機D色幾靚，即係影唔到本來顏色或者機身幫你調左，張相直出可能會討好D，但是否好相機我就有保留"},{"pid":"dfeb1667cf877c703e06de61a79daa4209912153","tid":296814,"uid":104387,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"